dct_description_sm: Zoning map of the Borough of Franklin Lakes by F. E. Harley, Civil Engineer printed as part of an official legal notice of the borough's amendment of an ordinance limitations and restrictions on development of the designated borough districts. Legend shows shading by industrial, business and residential districts. Map features signatures from the mayor, clerk and Zoning Commission chair in both 1937 and 1953.
